title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Plastics & Plastic Products
description: Imports of Intra EU - Plastics & Plastic Products in the United Kingdom decreased to 942 GBP Million in September from 973.77 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Plastics & Plastic Products in the United Kingdom averaged 622.50 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1110.55 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 268.64 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Plastics & Plastic Products.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
